    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=607864187825160759&sectionId=607891833489457750)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrDMipZEL0_text","label":"ggrDMipZEL0_text","default":"<p><strong>Why Your Doctor Probably Won't Tell You About This</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGPKVzypJa_text","label":"ggGPKVzypJa_text","default":"<p>Here's something Dr. Chen explained in his article that made me angry:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsHWfxFNT9_text","label":"ggsHWfxFNT9_text","default":"<p><strong>Big Pharma doesn't profit from helping your body heal itself.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmPcq9roro_text","label":"ggmPcq9roro_text","default":"<p>They profit from drugs you take forever. Drugs that manage symptoms but never fix the root cause.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvAhZSb5bu_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggvAhZSb5bu_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-19c2478b-c6e0-4f75-b8f0-f632bbbc1eb3.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggP_Jaaqt9C_text","label":"ggP_Jaaqt9C_text","default":"<p><strong>NAD+, Resveratrol, and Quercetin can't be patented.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBqQXn6g0u_text","label":"ggBqQXn6g0u_text","default":"<p>They're natural compounds. Anyone can use them. There's no 20-year patent protection. No billion-dollar exclusivity.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVekDk8PlF_text","label":"ggVekDk8PlF_text","default":"<p>So there's no financial incentive for drug companies to research them or for pharmaceutical reps to tell doctors about them.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gggjxH74zj5_text","label":"gggjxH74zj5_text","default":"<p><strong>It takes 17 years on average for new research to reach mainstream medical practice.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggd8lJcprb7_text","label":"ggd8lJcprb7_text","default":"<p>That's why the breakthrough research on NAD+ and bone health from Harvard Medical School and Stanford is happening right now, but your doctor hasn't mentioned it yet.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCiIyU4ffx_text","label":"ggCiIyU4ffx_text","default":"<p><strong>By the time your doctor learns about this, you could lose another 10-20% of your bone mass.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUKgp06TLp_text","label":"ggUKgp06TLp_text","default":"<p>That's permanent loss. Bone you can never fully regain.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCaoqptmnR_text","label":"ggCaoqptmnR_text","default":"<p><strong>I'm not saying doctors are bad. Mine genuinely didn't know there was another option.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8WDaJAmGQ_text","label":"gg8WDaJAmGQ_text","default":"<p>She was trained to prescribe the drugs the pharmaceutical reps tell her about. The ones with billion-dollar marketing budgets.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtdVtwu-6n_text","label":"ggtdVtwu-6n_text","default":"<p><strong>But waiting for the medical system to catch up could cost you your independence.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMCmz09tzE_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggMCmz09tzE_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-1bdfd65c-47bc-4b77-b049-cb3d52d192de.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4O_K1gq0W_text","label":"gg4O_K1gq0W_text","default":"<p><strong>How To Get Thryve</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1Tuqb4glh_text","label":"gg1Tuqb4glh_text","default":"<p><i><strong>&nbsp;(Before It Sells Out Again)</strong></i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnYF_Z1inD_text","label":"ggnYF_Z1inD_text","default":"<p>Dr. Chen's company produces Thryve in small batches to maintain quality control and ensure every bottle contains exactly what the label promises.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-Ky6vGwm8_text","label":"gg-Ky6vGwm8_text","default":"<p>To protect that standard, Thryve is sold exclusively through the official website at Thirmik.com.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTn0ab66UB_text","label":"ggTn0ab66UB_text","default":"<p>It’s not available on Amazon, eBay, or any third-party marketplaces, because selling direct is the only way they can guarantee proper handling, verified testing, and U.S. manufacturing oversight.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_q9K6Y17-_text","label":"gg_q9K6Y17-_text","default":"<p><strong>Because of this, they sell out regularly. Not because of artificial scarcity, but:</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggg2Qr1agE8_text","label":"ggg2Qr1agE8_text","default":"<p><strong>1.</strong> Small-batch production in the USA, using premium ingredients takes time.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggONTxCTq8O_text","label":"ggONTxCTq8O_text","default":"<p><strong>2. </strong>Each batch undergoes rigorous testing for purity &amp; quality (adds 2-3 weeks to production).</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5qKG-N7Xn_text","label":"gg5qKG-N7Xn_text","default":"<p><strong>3.</strong> Word is spreading fast among women who are tired of being told calcium or drugs are their only option.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwTfxSRn8v_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggwTfxSRn8v_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-6ca8e608-320c-4768-9b29-ee8eba4c9af4_1.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_LKuKoy1S_text","label":"gg_LKuKoy1S_text","default":"<p>Right now, they're offering a special bundle for women who want to commit to the full 90-day protocol:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxIk44MJII_text","label":"ggxIk44MJII_text","default":"<p><strong>Order 2 bottles, get 1 free on them + &nbsp;free shipping.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggc_zBuCe7t_text","label":"ggc_zBuCe7t_text","default":"<p>That's enough for three months. The same timeline that changed everything for me.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gguidrOix3h_text","label":"gguidrOix3h_text","default":"<p>Here's what you need to know:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8_NqrSxUs_text","label":"gg8_NqrSxUs_text","default":"<p><strong>This isn't a quick fix. Your bones didn't weaken overnight. They won't rebuild overnight either.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggC8wv5l6aV_text","label":"ggC8wv5l6aV_text","default":"<p>But if you give your body the cellular energy it needs for 90 days, you can measure the difference on your next scan.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_ZsyMABLk_text","label":"gg_ZsyMABLk_text","default":"<p><strong>Just like I did. Just like Linda, Jennifer, and Patricia did.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9HhpUAp7t_text","label":"gg9HhpUAp7t_text","default":"<p>The science is published. The results are real. The question is whether you're willing to try something your doctor hasn't told you about yet.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggs0tTHtAvI_text","label":"ggs0tTHtAvI_text","default":"<p><strong>The 90-Day Guarantee That Removes All Risk</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnUFwS8AGB_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggnUFwS8AGB_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/gempages_481559650848736414-5b152c85-78d4-4510-bb75-c0dfdb0a78df.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFrwrbNV33_text","label":"ggFrwrbNV33_text","default":"<p>Dr. Chen's company offers something no drug company ever would:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQCtovu_KU_text","label":"ggQCtovu_KU_text","default":"<p><strong>Try Thryve for 90 days. If you see 0 improvement in the way you feel or your next bone scan doesn't show improvement, they'll refund every penny.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggm_JdkSO5V_text","label":"ggm_JdkSO5V_text","default":"<p>No questions asked. No hassle. No keeping the bottles or jumping through hoops. They can offer this because the science works.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggU7R4YoONt_text","label":"ggU7R4YoONt_text","default":"<p>When you restore cellular energy, activate bone-building genes, and calm inflammation, your body knows what to do.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwMAqG6-oz_text","label":"ggwMAqG6-oz_text","default":"<p><strong>The only risk is doing nothing and losing more bone mass while you wait for a better option that isn't coming.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtloRvq-MA_text","label":"ggtloRvq-MA_text","default":"<p>Think about it: What does your doctor's option offer?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggex25Qn53K_text","label":"ggex25Qn53K_text","default":"<p>Bisphosphonates with no guarantee they'll work. A long list of terrifying side effects. And if they don't work or you can't tolerate them, you're back where you started - but with weaker bones.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0FZk4bBKE_text","label":"gg0FZk4bBKE_text","default":"<p><strong>Thryve offers you a genuine 90-day trial with your money back if it doesn't deliver.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvCmp6mIbU_text","label":"ggvCmp6mIbU_text","default":"<p>That's the difference between a company that profits from keeping you dependent on drugs forever, and a company that stands behind its science.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHxWAtfoI5_text","label":"ggHxWAtfoI5_text","default":"<p><strong>And The Best Part?</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLZcvaU0Km_text","label":"ggLZcvaU0Km_text","default":"<p>Thryve's simple and natural formula works at the cellular level, meaning it won’t interfere with any medications, treatments, or supplements you're currently taking.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglM-fjkcrX_text","label":"gglM-fjkcrX_text","default":"<p><strong>Thanks to NAD+, your body actually gains the energy it needs to fully utilize your bone-supporting supplements like calcium, magnesium, vitamin D3, and K2 to their full potential.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdCDB6rL3Z_text","label":"ggdCDB6rL3Z_text","default":"<p>Just three powerhouse ingredients, encased in an easy-to-swallow vegetable capsule. Made right here in the USA and shipped straight to your door.</p>"}],
